data.description: Open house Sunday Feb. 4th 2-3pm. Amazing home has 4 bedroom 3 1/2 bath, main floor laundry, partially finished basement, attached two car garage with a fenced back yard. (Hard to find! A bath on every floor!!) You'll fall in love with this home upon entry. Spacious open bright living room has new paint and luxury vinyl plank flooring. Living room is also open to the chef's kitchen. Kitchen has a dining area with a slider for easy access to the back deck for spring grilling. Large kitchen has granite countertops, stainless appliances, gas stove, and an abundance of kitchen cabinets. Mud room area & main floor laundry is off the kitchen. Upstairs is a grand master bedroom with a private bath and a walk-in closet. The other three bedrooms are also up, and all are good sized with plenty of closet space. The basement has a finished entertainment room with a full bath down. Egress window for a possible 5th bedroom too. Huge storage area and it is plumbed for a possible wet bar. The backyard is also another entertainment area with a patio and totally fenced. Plus, resort style living including community pool, splash park, big wheel track, soccer fields, club house, walking trails and open spaces. Enjoy this beautiful home and Centennial community today!
